	<article>
		
		<!-- Aside -->
				<!-- //Aside -->

		<section class="article-intro clearfix">
			
			
			
			<h1><a href="http://www.ralli.fi" target="_self">Ralli Oy (Ltd.)</a></h1>
<p>Welcome to <a href="/about-us/company">RALLI OY (Ltd.)</a>. We are a Finland based company with more than 30 years of experience in industrial <a href="/products-services/evaporators">Evaporators</a>&nbsp;and <a href="/products-services/dryers">Dryers</a>.&nbsp;We are experts at <a href="/products-services/evaporators#multiple-effect-evaporator">multiple-effect evaporators</a> using both <a href="/products-services/evaporators#tvr">thermal vapor re-compression (TVR)</a> and <a href="/products-services/evaporators#mvr">mechanical vapor re-compression (MVR)</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/products-services/evaporators#falling-film-evaporator">falling film evaporators</a>, rising film evaporators, forced circulation evaporators, spin dryers (<a href="/products-services/dryers#single-stage-spray-dryer">single-</a> and <a href="/products-services/dryers#multiple-stage-spray-dryer">multiple-stage</a>), ring dryers, fluidized-bed dryers and so on.&nbsp;Our scope varies from simple modifications of existing equipment to complete turn-key based projects.&nbsp;We have done numerous projects in Europe, Asia and Australia.&nbsp;Do not hesitate to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>!</p>		</section>

		
	</article>
